The spacing components on this page are used as reference for spacing tokens in the design system which can be found in storybook here: https://radius-ds.netlify.com/?path=/docs/foundations-other-tokens--space

The spacing tokens are Intended to be used for margin, padding, grid gaps, positioning and other layout-related CSS properties. This is an intentional constraint that makes it difficult to add one-off or in-between sizes that could lead to unwanted and rippling affects to layout.

See component pages to see how it is used.
